<L>__{exterior market place (day) medium shot}
<A>__{a closer, level shot, the camera panning, shows, the two breathless men closing in on each other. as they reach an intersection in the streets, lighted by a shaft of sunlight, the new arab comes up behind the original man being chased and whipping out a knife from under his robes, plunges it into the back of the first man. then he turns and quickly moves away into a street on his left. the first arab jerks his head up and backward with the sharp pain of the stabbing, then he staggers into the dark shadows.}
